  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.biome_blocks.name": "生物群系方块",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.biome_blocks.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)生物群系方块[#]()是一类建筑方块，能够[#](00AAAA)自我着色以匹配所在的生物群系[#]()。",
