  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.chat_detector.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.chat_detector.name": "聊天探测器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.chat_detector.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)聊天探测器[#]()会在其所有者发送特定聊天消息时输出一个红石信号脉冲。\\\n  \\\n使用该方块会打开其界面，可在其中一个输入[#](00AAAA)正则表达式模式[#]()用于检测所有者发送的每一条消息。\\\n  \\\n当然，无需使用过于高深的正则表达式。例如，正则表达式“example”会匹配所有包含“example”的聊天消息。\\\n  \\\n放置该方块的玩家会自动成为其所有者。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.chat_detector.page_0.title": "聊天探测器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.chat_detector.page_1.text": "在其菜单中，也可以选择[#](00AAAA)拦截[#]()目标消息。\\\n  \\\n启用该功能时，匹配的消息实际不会发送到聊天栏，但仍会输出红石脉冲。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.chat_detector.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_button.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_button.name": "接触式按钮",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_button.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)接触式按钮[#]()的功能类似于石头按钮，但相较于直接点击_它本身_，你需要点击其指向的方块。\\\n  \\\n也就是说，如果接触式按钮朝上放置，那么点击它上方的方块，即可使其发出红石信号。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_button.page_0.title": "接触式按钮",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_lever.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_lever.name": "接触式拉杆",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_lever.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)接触式拉杆[#]()的功能类似于拉杆，但相较于直接点击_它本身_，你需要点击其指向的方块。\\\n  \\\n也就是说，如果接触式拉杆朝上放置，那么点击它上方的方块，即可使其发出红石信号。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.contact_lever.page_0.title": "接触式拉杆",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.global_chat_detector.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.global_chat_detector.name": "全局聊天探测器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.global_chat_detector.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)全局聊天探测器[#]()的功能类似于[聊天探测器](entry://blocks/chat_detector)，但会作用于所有玩家。\\\n  \\\n在其菜单中，你可以放置最多9张[身份卡](entry://items/id_card)。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.global_chat_detector.page_0.title": "全局聊天探测器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.global_chat_detector.page_1.text": "如果全局聊天探测器设置为拦截消息，它将拦截由身份卡指定的玩家所发送的消息。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.global_chat_detector.page_1.title": "",
