  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.pitcher_plant.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)猪笼草[#]()是一种[#](00AAAA)可以充当无限水源[#]()的花。\\\n  \\\n同时它还会偶尔会用水[#](00AAAA)填充相邻的储罐[#]()！",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.pitcher_plant.page_0.title": "猪笼草",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.pitcher_plant.page_1.text": "可以在含有标签[#](00AAAA)#c:is_wet/overworld[#]()的生物群系中找到猪笼草，尤其是沼泽和丛林",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.pitcher_plant.page_1.title": "",
