  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.shock_absorber.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)冲击吸收器[#]()可以[#](00AAAA)完全吸收摔落伤害[#]()。\\\n  \\\n此外，摔落高度越高，其发出的红石信号强度就越高。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.blocks.shock_absorber.page_0.title": "冲击吸收器",
