  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.blaze_and_steel.page_0.title": "烈焰打火石",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.block_mover.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.block_mover.name": "方块搬运器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.block_mover.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)方块搬运器[#]()可以[#](00AAAA)捡起并重新放置方块[#]()，方块实体会被保留！\\\n  \\\n右击一个方块可以将它捡起来，再次右击地面可以重新放置。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.block_mover.page_0.title": "方块搬运器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.block_mover.page_1.text": "不可破坏的方块、或带有#irregular_implements:block_mover_blacklist的方块等，无法通过方块搬运器捡起。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.block_mover.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.bottle_of_air.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.bottle_of_air.name": "空气瓶",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.bottle_of_air.page_0.text": "在水下使用[#](AA00AA)空气瓶[#]()可以重新填满氧气条。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.bottle_of_air.page_0.title": "空气瓶",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.bottle_of_air.page_1.text": "可以在[#](00AAAA)海底神殿[#]()内找到。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.bottle_of_air.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.chunk_analyzer.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.chunk_analyzer.name": "区块分析器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.chunk_analyzer.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)区块分析器[#]()能够用来[#](00AAAA)扫描区块的内容[#]()。\\\n  \\\n右击可以打开一个菜单，里面会列举区块内的所有方块以及它们各自的数量。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.chunk_analyzer.page_0.title": "区块分析器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.chunk_analyzer.page_1.text": "也能展示区块内的全部[#](00AAAA)实体[#]()！",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.chunk_analyzer.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.divining_rod.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.divining_rod.name": "占卜法杖",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.divining_rod.page_0.text": "手持时，[#](AA00AA)占卜法杖[#]()可以[#](00AAAA)无视方块遮挡显示附近的矿石[#]()。\\\n  \\\n默认显示范围是20格以内，这一项可以另外配置。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.divining_rod.page_0.title": "占卜法杖",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.divining_rod.page_1.text": "[#](00AAAA)每种矿石[#]()都有一种对应的占卜法杖，还有一种占卜法杖可以显示[#](00AAAA)全部种类的矿石[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.divining_rod.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.drop_filter.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.drop_filter.name": "掉落物过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.drop_filter.page_0.text": "The [#](AA00AA)掉落物过滤器[#]()可以[#](00AAAA)防止特定的物品被捡起[#]()。\\\n  \\\n按下使用键可以打开菜单，然后可以添加[物品过滤器](entry://items/item_filter)。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.drop_filter.page_0.title": "掉落物过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.drop_filter.page_1.text": "[#](AA00AA)虚空掉落物过滤器[#]()的功能与它相似，不同之处在于它会[#](00AAAA)直接摧毁物品[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.drop_filter.page_1.title": "虚空掉落物过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.emerald_compass.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.emerald_compass.name": "绿宝石指南针",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.emerald_compass.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)绿宝石指南针[#]()可以用来定位玩家。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.emerald_compass.page_0.title": "绿宝石指南针",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.emerald_compass.page_1.text": "将它与一个[玩家过滤器](entry://items/player_filter)合成，指南针便会指向玩家过滤器所设置的玩家",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.emerald_compass.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.ender_bucket.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.ender_bucket.name": "末影桶",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.ender_bucket.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)末影桶[#]()即使在[#](00AAAA)对非源头的流体[#]()使用时，也能盛取流体源。\\\n  \\\n它会寻找最近的流体源方块，然后将它盛起。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.ender_bucket.page_0.title": "末影桶",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.ender_bucket.page_1.text": "[#](AA00AA)强化末影桶[#]()的功能与它相似，不同之处在于它[#](00AAAA)最多可以盛起10个流体源[#]()！",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.ender_bucket.page_1.title": "强化末影桶",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.entity_filter.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.entity_filter.name": "实体过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.entity_filter.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)实体过滤器[#]()可以在多种场合下用来过滤实体。\\\n  \\\n右击实体可以将它的类型存储到过滤器。没有看向实体时会设置实体类型为玩家。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.entity_filter.page_0.title": "实体过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.escape_rope.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.escape_rope.name": "逃生绳",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.escape_rope.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)逃生绳[#]()可以用来快速[#](00AAAA)传送出洞穴[#]()。\\\n  \\\n原理为寻路到可以向上看见天空的位置。\\\n  \\\n按住右键将持续搜索直到成功，或在充分时间后计作搜索失败。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.escape_rope.page_0.title": "逃生绳",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.escape_rope.page_1.text": "成功使用后，[#](FF5555)物品耐久将会消耗[#]()，使得可以使用最多20次。\\\n  \\\n使用失败后，物品会从手中掉出。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.escape_rope.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.evil_tear.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.evil_tear.name": "邪恶之泪",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.evil_tear.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)邪恶之泪[#]()可以用来制作[#](00AAAA)人造末地传送门[#]()。\\\n  \\\n你需要搭建3x3的末地石平台，在上方一格高度搭建5x5的黑曜石空心环。\\\n  \\\n在正中心末地石上方五格处的位置放置另一个末地石，在新放置的末地石下方放置一个末地烛。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.evil_tear.page_0.title": "邪恶之泪",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.evil_tear.page_1.text": "在末地烛上使用邪恶之泪可以开启传送门。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.evil_tear.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.grass_seeds.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.grass_seeds.name": "草籽",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.grass_seeds.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)草籽[#]()可以用来[#](00AAAA)扩散草皮[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.grass_seeds.page_0.title": "草籽",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.grass_seeds.page_1.text": "草籽拥有[#](AA00AA)16种颜色的变体[#]()，可以用来扩散带颜色的草皮。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.grass_seeds.page_1.title": "染色草籽",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.item_filter.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.item_filter.name": "物品过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.item_filter.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)物品过滤器[#]()可以在多种场合下用来过滤物品。\\\n  \\\n按下使用键打开菜单，当中有9个物品槽位。在槽位中放置一个物品即会加入筛选。\\\n  \\\n每个非空的物品槽位上有两个按钮。左侧按钮用来设置槽位筛选[#](00AAAA)物品[#]()还是[#](00AAAA)物品标签[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.item_filter.page_0.title": "物品过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.item_filter.page_1.text": "右侧按钮用于进行以下操作之一：\\\n  \\\n已设置为筛选物品时，可以设置是否需要物品有相同的[#](00AAAA)组件[#]()。\\\n  \\\n已设置为筛选过滤物品标签时，将在要筛选的标签间循环。\\\n  \\\n另外，在过滤器的右上方可以设置所有过滤器为[#](00AAAA)黑名单[#]()模式或[#](00AAAA)白名单[#]()模式。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.item_filter.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.location_filter.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.location_filter.name": "位置过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.location_filter.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)位置过滤器[#]()是一种用来表示世界中某一位置的物品。 \\\n  \\\n对方块使用可以将它的位置保存到过滤器。潜行右击可以清除。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.location_filter.page_0.title": "位置过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.location_filter.page_1.text": "手持时，当前设置的位置会显示出来！",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.location_filter.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.magic_hood.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.magic_hood.name": "魔法风帽",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.magic_hood.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)魔法风帽[#]()可以用来隐藏姓名标签和药水粒子。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.magic_hood.page_0.title": "魔法风帽",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.magic_hood.page_1.text": "只能在[#](00AAAA)地牢箱子[#]()或[#](00AAAA)村庄铁匠铺[#]()中找到。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.magic_hood.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.name": "物品",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.player_filter.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.player_filter.name": "玩家过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.player_filter.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)玩家过滤器[#]()可以用来[#](00AAAA)识别玩家身份[#]()。\\\n  \\\n对其他玩家使用会设置他们为目标，没有看向其他玩家时使用会设置自己为目标。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.player_filter.page_0.title": "玩家过滤器",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.portkey.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.portkey.name": "门钥匙",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.portkey.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)门钥匙[#]()可以绑定到一个位置，随后[#](00AAAA)如果有人捡到并丢出门钥匙，他就会被传送到这个位置[#]()。\\\n  \\\n在方块上使用可以设置传送的位置。丢出时，它会在短暂延迟后失去光效并激活。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.portkey.page_0.title": "门钥匙",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.portkey.page_1.text": "门钥匙可与任何其他物品合成从而获得[#](00AAAA)伪装效果[#]()，外观将变成对应物品的模样。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.portkey.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_anchor.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_anchor.name": "通灵锚",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_anchor.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)通灵锚[#]()能与任何物品合成，从而绑定物品，[#](00AAAA)在死亡后保留这些物品[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_anchor.page_0.title": "通灵锚",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_anchor.page_1.text": "物品复还后，[#](FF5555)通灵锚即被消耗[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_anchor.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_chestplate.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_chestplate.name": "通灵盔甲",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_chestplate.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)通灵盔甲[#]()性能与钻石盔甲相当，但[#](00AAAA)耐久度和附魔能力更优[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_chestplate.page_0.title": "通灵盔甲",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_chestplate.page_1.text": "还会让你略微变得透明！",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.spectre_chestplate.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.stable_ender_pearl.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.stable_ender_pearl.name": "稳态末影珍珠",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.stable_ender_pearl.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)稳态末影珍珠[#]()作用与寻常的末影珍珠并不相同。\\\n  \\\n右击时不会将它掷出，而是[#](00AAAA)将它绑定到自己[#]()。\\\n  \\\n丢出并等待一小段后，珍珠会[#](00AAAA)将你传送到这一位置[#]()。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.stable_ender_pearl.page_0.title": "稳态末影珍珠",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.stable_ender_pearl.page_1.text": "没有绑定任何实体时，珍珠会改为抓取10格范围里的一个随机实体，然后传送到自身位置。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.stable_ender_pearl.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.summoning_pendulum.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.summoning_pendulum.name": "召唤灵摆",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.summoning_pendulum.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)召唤灵摆[#]()可以用来捕捉并重新释放实体。\\\n  \\\n右击实体可以捡起，再次右击地面可以放出。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.summoning_pendulum.page_0.title": "召唤灵摆",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.summoning_pendulum.page_1.text": "可以在[#](00AAAA)地牢箱子[#]()中找到。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.summoning_pendulum.page_1.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.void_stone.description": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.void_stone.name": "虚空石",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.void_stone.page_0.text": "[#](AA00AA)虚空石[#]()的本质是一个便携式垃圾桶。\\\n  \\\n在它的菜单内放入的任何物品都会被删除。",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.items.void_stone.page_0.title": "",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.name": "Irregular Implements模组指南",
  "book.irregular_implements.guide.tooltip": "一本用来通晓万物的指南"

}